    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. While the car is mechanically sound and drives well, the exterior shows its age with several visible scratches and minor dings. The interior also shows typical wear and tear on the upholstery and carpets consistent with its history. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a fair price point.",
